details:
</p>
fifth successor on the throne (<a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/2324">gaddī</a>) of <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/1">Bhagavantanātha</a> in <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/3">Rānāgāũ</a>;
