</p>
-a <a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/41">bā̃dhā</a> in <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/2039">Ḍāḍā</a> in the <a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/849">ambala</a> of <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/343">Phalabang</a> (<a href="/nepal/books/viewitem/92">Naraharinātha VS 2022</a>: 461, K_0469_0023, see also K_0469_0017 [doc. 5]);
