met <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/2136">Henry Ambrose Oldfield</a> in February 1854 at <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/386">Thāpāthalī</a> (<a href="/nepal/books/viewitem/115">Oldfield 1880</a>, 1: 267).
