<p/>
in 1810 (VS 1867), ordered to examine (together with <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/2035">Jyūṃdhana Khatrī</a> and  <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/2036">Raghuvira Rānā</a>) the [corresponding] documents and, if ascertained to be correct, confirm the <a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/932">guṭha</a> <a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/1898">birtā</a>s that were given by the kings of <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/6">Salyan</a> to <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/1">Bhagavantanātha</a> (<a href="/nepal/books/viewitem/92">Naraharinātha VS 2022</a>: 460, see also the summary of the <a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/992">lālamohara</a> in K_0469_0017 [[doc. 15]]);
<p/>
<a href="/nepal/words/viewitem/1109">subbā</a> of <a href="/nepal/ontologies/viewitem/17">Jumla</a> in 1817 (VS 1874, K_0093_0002W).
